## Risk register

- Collectors that currently don't produce a well-structured snapshot may
  need a small adapter. If so, the extractor returns an empty list and
  we note which collector was shallow.
- Schedule cadence table seed may conflict with future settings sync
  (the seed runs once on init). Idempotent via `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING`.
- First deploy will emit a burst of `facts_upserted_total{action="insert"}`
  as all collectors populate on their first poll. Expected; do not
  interpret as volume.


